markets.guidance:
Winner

Predict the winner of the match at *Regular time.

The following options are available:

  •  Home bet wins if Home team wins the match.
  •  Away bet wins if Away team wins the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.

  •  Home bet wins if Home team player wins the Nth set.
  •  Away bet wins if Away team player wins the Nth set.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.

Games O/U

Predict will the match have more or less games than the given line. *Regular time

The following options are available(For example Ov/Un 15.5):

  •  Over 15.5 bet wins if there are 16 or more games in the match.
  •  Under 15.5 bet wins if there are 15 or less games in the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
Game Handicap

Predict who will win the most game after the allotted game handicap is applied.*Regular time

The following options are available(For example 0.5):

  •  Home(+0.5) bet wins if Home team wins more game or equal with Away team.
  •  Away(-0.5) bet wins if Away wins at least one game.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.

markets.guidance:
Home to win a set

Predict if home player win at least a set. *Regular time

The following options are available:

  •  Yes bet wins if home player wins at least one set.
  •  No bet wins if home player loses all sets in the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Home to win a set

markets.guidance:
Away to win a set

Predict if away player win at least a set. *Regular time

The following options are available:

  •  Yes bet wins if away player wins at least one set.
  •  No bet wins if away player loses all sets in the match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Away to win a set

markets.guidance:
Any set to nil

Predict if there is 6:0 or 0:6 in a set. *Regular time

The following options are available:

  •  Yes bet wins if there is 6:0 or 0:6 in a set.
  •  No bet wins if there is other score(not 6:0 or 0:6) in every set.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Any set to nil

markets.guidance:
Odd/Even games

Predict if the number of games played during the match is odd or even. *Regular time

The following options are available:

  •  Odd bet wins if the number of games played during the match is an odd number(1,3,5...)
  •  Even bet wins if the number of games played during the match is an even number(0,2,4...)

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Odd/even games

markets.guidance:
Correct score

Predict what is correct score. *Regular time

The following options are available:

  •  6:0 bet wins if the correct score is 6:0.

    • ......

  •  5:6 bet wins if the correct score is 5:6.

    • ......

  •  Other bet wins if the correct score is others.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Correct score

markets.guidance:
Double result (1st set/match)

Predict which team player wins the first set and entire match. *Regular time

The following options are available:

  •  Home/Home bet wins if Home team player wins the first set and entire match.
  •  Away/Home bet wins if Away team player wins the first set and Home team player wins the entire match.
  •  Home/Away bet wins if Home team player wins the first set and Away team player wins the entire match.
  •  Away/Away bet wins if Away team player wins the first set and entire match.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its regular time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Double result (1st set/match)

markets.guidance:
Winner & O/U

Combo:Winner at full time & total points over/under the given line.

The following options are available(for example O/U 22.5):

  •  Home & Over 22.5 bet wins if Home wins the match and the number of total points at full time is 23 or more.
  •  Away & Over 22.5 bet wins if Away wins the match and the number of total points at full time is 23 or more.
  •  Home & Under 22.5 bet wins if Home wins the match and the number of total points at full time is less than 23.
  •  Away & Under 22.5 bet wins if Away wins the match and the number of total points at full time is less than 23.

* Bets on this market are settled on the result of the match at the end of its full time including all injury and stoppage time.
markets.name: Winner & O/U
